flask-loggger: A server that logs requests,
ideally the headers, cookies, and body of requests.

TO BUILD:
docker build -t 'flask_logger' .

RUN:
docker run -d -p8001:8000 jrd mod_wsgi-express start-server --user www-data --group www-data --log-to-terminal wsgi.py




inspiration:
https://stackoverflow.com/a/44013423/37176

flask documentation  http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/1.0/
flask request object http://flask.pocoo.org/docs/1.0/api/#incoming-request-data

catch all url: http://flask.pocoo.org/snippets/57/
